n meetup <a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/guida-ai-meetup-di-wordpress/\">leggi qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tutti i meetup WordPress italiani attivi sono <a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/\">elencati qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nei prossimi giorni, <em>in ordine cronologico</em>, si incontrano le community di:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cagliari</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 3 lug, ore 19:00, &#8220;Programma di Mentorship WordPress: Unisciti alla Comunit&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/cagliari-wordpress-meetup/events/301707922\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Zagarolo</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 10 lug, ore 18:00, &#8220;Meet &amp; Greet&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/zagarolo-wordpress-meetup/events/301794445\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Milano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 10 lug, ore 20:00, &#8220;Pizza!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/301830289\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Terni</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 18 lug, ore 19:00, &#8220;Pizza!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-terni/events/301916469\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Torino</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 18 lug, ore 19:00, &#8220;Il valore del proprio lavoro&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-torino/events/301773190\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lecce</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 19 lug, ore 18:00, &#8220;Ottimizziamo un sito web da zero&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-lecce/events/302015457\" t